{"tid":2394397,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大博物館稱發現重要原住民文物　藝術家：100% 肯定是我的作品","createTime":"2021-02-04T06:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T07:35:10.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"67da4af70742fee1fa44e6c6c77c6574c609983d","tid":2394397,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:53:22.000Z","msg":"加拿大博物館稱發現重要原住民文物　藝術家：100% 肯定是我的作品<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%A8%E7%A8%B1%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%8F%E6%B0%91%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9-%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93%E5%AE%B6-100-%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9A%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81/?fbclid=IwAR0jbAwtZnbiuCxIRr5YjnDuQBbpPnl8s7oaFhW_spzPRsLKJ7Qh7YncItc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%258E%259F%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%2589%25A9-%25E8%2597%259D%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%25AE%25B6-100-%25E8%2582%25AF%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2593%2581%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0jbAwtZnbiuCxIRr5YjnDuQBbpPnl8s7oaFhW_spzPRsLKJ7Qh7YncItc&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=990f7b63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%258E%259F%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%2589%25A9-%25E8%2597%259D%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%25AE%25B6-100-%25E8%2582%25AF%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2593%2581%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0jbAwtZnbiuCxIRr5YjnDuQBbpPnl8s7oaFhW_spzPRsLKJ7Qh7YncItc&h=0641a243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%A8%E7%A8%B1%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%8F%E6%B0%91%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9-%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93%E5%AE%B6-100-%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9A%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81/?fbclid=IwAR0jbAwtZnbiuCxIRr5YjnDuQBbpPnl8s7oaFhW_spzPRsLKJ7Qh7YncItc</a><br />\n<br />\n加拿大皇家不列顛哥倫比亞博物館（Royal BC Museum）上週指去年在海灘發現一根雕花石柱，相信該石柱是當地原住民重要的儀式性文物，更形容這次是「標誌性發現」。該石柱表面雖已佈滿藻類，但可見其人臉雕刻圖案。然而，近日當地藝術家 Ray Boudreau 表示石柱是他的作品，並非原住民工藝品。他強調：「我可以100%肯定這是我的作品」。<br />\n<br />\nBoudreau 向當地媒體CTV表示該石柱是他在2017年創作的雕刻品，並向記者展示了其iPhone上面一張時間標示為2017年1月23日的照片，圖中石柱與博物館發現的石柱十分相似。<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">Boudreau 表示，當年用了三天時間在另一個海灘雕刻的作品，但作品還沒徹底完成就不見了，還以為是被偷走。<br />\n<br />\n最早看到博物館發現石柱的新聞時，他也不知道是否該出面澄清，反問：「你覺得我應該說任何東西嗎？我僅僅擁有它三天，然後它就自己長出腿跑掉了」。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但後來因不想說謊，並認為大眾應該要知道真相，Boudreau 便主動聯繫博物館及媒體交代事件。他說：「我可以100%肯定這是我的作品」。他向記者仔細描述自己的作品特徵，「我在眼底刻了幾條奇特的線，而且嘴唇是如此獨特，就像指紋一樣」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>博物館：將安排與Boudreau會面</strong><br />\n<br />\n針對這次事件，博物館向 The Art Newspaper 表示，將與當地原住民社群組織 Songhees Nation及Esquimalt Nation 和Boudreau 會面，相信雙方溝通過後可較清楚地估計需要多少時間去判斷石柱的來源。<br />\n<br />\n博物館的原住民館藏負責人 Lou-ann Neel 另表示，該雕刻石柱本身被相當厚的藻類覆蓋，因此很難看到所有圖案並確定它是近期的雕刻品，抑或是古老雕刻。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">博物館上週發聲明指在維多利亞地區海灘上一根雕花石柱，又稱經策展人和考古學家初步判斷石柱可追溯至1880年代，可能為當地原住民重要的儀式性文物。該石柱被發現時已佈滿藻類，重約100公斤。館方更形容這次是 「標誌性發現」。當地媒體亦大肆報道。然而，在 Boudreau 指石柱為其雕刻作品後，博物館聲明已從官方網站上下架。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"409c326f231809e056a748b061c8881bcafcd09e","tid":2394397,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:53:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200203-18_NYJsr_1200x0.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200203-18_NYJsr_1200x0.png&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=368582f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200203-18_NYJsr_1200x0.png&h=8dfe9381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200203-18_NYJsr_1200x0.png</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjd1hUd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxjd1hUd.png&h=a95d809a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"975dfa95c629e7b94796411162f97fafaaeeede2","tid":2394397,"uid":105715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:55:51.000Z","msg":"相信雙方溝通過後可較清楚地估計需要多少時間去判斷石柱的來源。<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野中文嚟？"},{"pid":"6cc8259a4ee10c3163aed7bca68f23a39e7dc49e","tid":2394397,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:59:37.000Z","msg":"碳14！"},{"pid":"589bf1d5f02a629220434c94f2ac149a015b5510","tid":2394397,"uid":317956,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6cc8259a4ee10c3163aed7bca68f23a39e7dc49e","tid":2394397,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:59:37.000Z","msg":"碳14！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T07:32:21.000Z","msg":"石頭點碳14"},{"pid":"43cbb921071698cadf4f9ab471923d89b959be27","tid":2394397,"uid":40499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"589bf1d5f02a629220434c94f2ac149a015b5510","tid":2394397,"uid":317956,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6cc8259a4ee10c3163aed7bca68f23a39e7dc49e","tid":2394397,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:59:37.000Z","msg":"碳14！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T07:32:21.000Z","msg":"石頭點碳14"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T07:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />舊石頭岩岩生出黎"}]}